query: SELECT CASE WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, data_nascimento, CURDATE()) < 18 THEN '0-17 anos' WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, data_nascimento, CURDATE()) BETWEEN 18 AND 30 THEN '18-30 anos' ELSE 'Outro' END as nome, COUNT(*) as valor FROM pacientes WHERE tenant_id = 1 AND deleted_at IS NULL GROUP BY 1 LIMIT 5;
